data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautiful well loved home in a wonderful neighborhood. You'll fall in love with this beauty upon entry. Newer interior paint, updated kitchen and laundry with an added stylish barn door and all appliances included. As you start walking in you'll feel the calming, light and bright living room that leads into the dining, kitchen and family room. Plentily of room to entertain family and friends. Primary Suite gives a peaceful relaxing feeling with private bath. Walk out back to a serene fully fenced yard for those wonderful BBQ's or sit with a cup coffee/tea and wake up with the birds chirping and squirrels chasing and get ready for your day!!
